<div class="container">
    <h2>About NutritionApp</h2>
    <p>NutritionApp is an application that helps you track your nutrition and achieve your dietary and health goals.</p>

    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
    <p>Our mission is to enable users to easily track their nutrition, make healthy choices, and achieve their dietary goals.</p>

    <h3>Main Features</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Tracking food and beverage intake</li>
        <li>Automatic calculation of nutritional values</li>
        <li>Reviewing past intake</li>
        <li>Ability to edit foods in past diaries and delete previous diaries</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Technologies Used</h3>
    <p>NutritionApp is developed using the Microsoft .NET Core framework for the backend, ASP.NET Core for the web application, Entity Framework Core for database access, and Bootstrap for the user interface design.</p>

